            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Sextus Nonius Africanus, son of Sextus, of tribe Quirina [...] lived for 28 years. To Caecilia Zotica, Sextus Nonius Albanus made this for his excellent wife. One sestertius per person [was provided] for a banquet worthy of her.</p>
